<LI class=text>Want a general history about CES? <A href="/docs/2009_CES_Fact_Sheet_-_4.16.pdf" target=_blank>Try the CES Fact Sheet (pdf)</A>. </LI>
<LI class=text>Interested in CES on social networking sites? Find <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/facebook" target=_blank>CES on Facebook</A>, <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/twitter" target=_blank>Twitter</A>, <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/youtube" target=_blank>YouTube</A> and <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/flickr" target=_blank>Flickr</A>. </LI>
<LI class=text>Want to tap into CES connections all year? <A href="/myCES.asp">Try the MyCES Personal Planner.</A> </LI>
<LI class=text>And as always, check <A href="http://www.cesweb.org/" target=_blank>CESweb.org</A> each week for breaking news about the upcoming show, January 8-11, 2009, in Las Vegas, Nevada. <A href="https://cms.ce.org/register">Register for the 2009 CES.</A></LI></UL>    
